Sally Lightfoot crab model (sally.glb / grapsus_grapsus_crab_280.blend)
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Purchased from Superhive (Blender Market). Royalty-free for use in a shipped
product, but redistribution of the source asset is not permitted — so it is not
committed here. When the asset is absent the body falls back to a procedural
capsule stand-in crab — same joints, sim, and training, shown as the Rapier debug
wireframe — so `cargo build`, `cargo run`, and `cargo test` all work with no purchase.

To use the model if you own it, fetch it into `assets/` (gitignored):

    scripts/fetch-sally.sh        # pulls from the private bddap-bot/rl-assets release

then run with `CRAB_MODEL_PATH=sally.glb`. The Steam demo binary may bake the
model in (incorporated into the product, which the license allows); the loose
file never enters this public repo.
